data.value: Little Caesars has will always strive to drive the best pizza in the world! We source our ingredients from Canadian farmers with utmost quality. Our dough is made from the highest quality flour and is set to rest for up to a week for the best consistency. We make sure that everyone has access to our products at the most valuable price. We will continue to show the world what god food is meant to taste like!
